{"word":"H7563 - רָשָׁע - râshâʻ - raw-shaw' - Condemned","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָשָׁע</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>râshâʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>raw-shaw'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Condemned"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"குற்றவாளியான, குற்றஞ்சுமந்த, துஷ்டனான, பாவியான, துன்மார்க்கனான, அநியாயஞ் செய்கிறவனான, ஆகாதவனான, பொல்லாத மனுஷனான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"wicked, criminal"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/H7561 - רָשַׁע - râshaʻ - raw-shah'/7561\">H7561</a>; morally <i>wrong</i>; concretely an (actively) <i>bad</i> person: -  + condemned, guilty, ungodly, wicked (man), that did wrong."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4849 - מִרְשַׁעַת - mirshaʻath - meer-shah'-ath/4849\">H4849</a>, <a href=\"#/H7561 - רָשַׁע - râshaʻ - raw-shah'/7561\">H7561</a>, <a href=\"#/H7562 - רֶשַׁע - reshaʻ - reh'-shah/7562\">H7562</a>, <a href=\"#/H7563 - רָשָׁע - râshâʻ - raw-shaw'/7563\">H7563</a>, <a href=\"#/H7564 - רִשְׁעָה - rishʻâh - rish-aw'/7564\">H7564</a>"}]}